
  Spheal    Ice Type Pokémon

  SPHEAL is much faster rolling 
  than  walking to get around. 
   When groups of Spheal 
  eat, they all clap at once to 
  show their pleasure.  Because 
  of this, their mealtimes are 
  noisy. 
